Package: ABSSeq
Type: Package
Title: ABSSeq: a new RNA-Seq analysis method based on modelling absolute
    expression differences
Version: 1.22.6
Author: Wentao Yang
Maintainer: Wentao Yang <wyang@zoologie.uni-kiel.de>
Description: Inferring differential expression genes by absolute counts
    difference between two groups, utilizing Negative binomial distribution
    and moderating fold-change according to heterogeneity of dispersion across
    expression level.
License: GPL (>= 3)
biocViews: DifferentialExpression
Imports:
    locfit,
    limma
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10),
    methods
Suggests: edgeR
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
